description: Returns information about a kdb changeset.

parameters.name: environmentId
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the kdb environment.

parameters.name: databaseName
parameters.description: The name of the kdb database.

parameters.name: changesetId
parameters.description: A unique identifier of the changeset for which you want to retrieve data.

nested_items.name: changesetId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the changeset.

nested_items.name: databaseName
nested_items.description: The name of the kdb database.

nested_items.name: environmentId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the kdb environment.

nested_items.name: changeRequests
nested_items.description: A list of change request objects that are run in order.

nested_items.name: changeType
nested_items.description: Defines the type of change request. A changeType can have the following values:
PUT --- Adds or updates files in a database.
DELETE --- Deletes files in a database.

nested_items.name: s3Path
nested_items.description: Defines the S3 path of the source file that is required to add or update files in a database.

nested_items.name: dbPath
nested_items.description: Defines the path within the database directory.

nested_items.name: createdTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp at which the changeset was created in FinSpace. The value is determined as epoch time in milliseconds. For example, the value for Monday, November 1, 2021 12:00:00 PM UTC is specified as 1635768000000.

nested_items.name: activeFromTimestamp
nested_items.description: Beginning time from which the changeset is active. The value is determined as epoch time in milliseconds. For example, the value for Monday, November 1, 2021 12:00:00 PM UTC is specified as 1635768000000.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp at which the changeset was updated in FinSpace. The value is determined as epoch time in milliseconds. For example, the value for Monday, November 1, 2021 12:00:00 PM UTC is specified as 1635768000000.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: Status of the changeset creation process.
Pending --- Changeset creation is pending.
Processing --- Changeset creation is running.
Failed --- Changeset creation has failed.
Complete --- Changeset creation has succeeded.

nested_items.name: errorInfo
nested_items.description: Provides details in the event of a failed flow, including the error type and the related error message.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: Specifies the error message that appears if a flow fails.

nested_items.name: errorType
nested_items.description: Specifies the type of error.
